OL,3,CThe Jersey International Motoring
OL,4,CFestival returns for 2026
OL,6,FThe Jersey International Motoring
OL,7,FFestival is returning this week with
OL,8,Ffive days of celebrations and
OL,9,Fdemonstrations.
OL,11,FDespite the rainy weather last year,
OL,12,Fthe event attracted thousands of
OL,13,Fspectators to watch their favourite
OL,14,Fvehicles in roadshows and speeding
OL,15,Fdown Victoria Avenue.
OL,17,FFor the first time, the festival is
OL,18,Frunning over five days, with a launch
OL,19,Fevent taking place at People's Park
OL,20,Ftoday (Wednesday 3 May).
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/9
