OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1780513862
OL,3,CThe Jersey International Motoring
OL,4,CFestival returns for 2026
OL,6,FOrganisers say the launch showcases
OL,7,F"the public's favourite vehicles from
OL,8,Fthe festival", parading them through
OL,9,Ftown.
OL,11,FThe festivities are scheduled to
OL,12,Fcontinue until Sunday 7 June,
OL,13,Ffeaturing "spectacular visual
OL,14,Fshowcases", from rolling roadshows to
OL,15,Fa #30 million Jaguar.
OL,17,FWhat is the Jersey International
OL,18,FMotoring Festival?
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
