OL,3,CThe Jersey International Motoring
OL,4,CFestival returns for 2026
OL,6,FThe festival is one of the two major
OL,7,Fannual events organised by the Classic
OL,8,FVintage and Modern Racing Club of
OL,9,FJersey.
OL,11,FHosting its first event at the
OL,12,Fbeginning of the millennium, it has
OL,13,Fnow grown into a free event for
OL,14,Fislanders to enjoy, attracting
OL,15,Ftourists and guest motors to the
OL,16,Fisland.
OL,18,F"Members never race to win trophies
OL,19,Fbut only for the pleasure of perhaps
OL,20,Fimproving on their previous best
OL,21,Ftimes," the Club states.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
