OL,3,CThe Jersey International Motoring
OL,4,CFestival returns for 2026
OL,6,F"Inspiration for the event stems from
OL,7,Fthe Jersey International Road Race
OL,8,Fthat ran between 1947 and 1952;
OL,9,FJersey's rich history in Motorsport
OL,10,Fallows aspects of almost every
OL,11,Fdiscipline of motoring into the event."
OL,13,FWhat's happening this year?
OL,15,FThursday 4 June will see a "rolling
OL,16,Froadshow" of cars from across
OL,17,Finternational motorsport and the
OL,18,Fisland along Victoria Avenue.
OL,20,FLocal drivers can show their cars off
OL,21,Fnext to high-speed displays.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
