PN,38205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1780513862
OL,3,CThe Jersey International Motoring
OL,4,CFestival returns for 2026
OL,6,FIslanders and visitors alike can view
OL,7,Fthe cars on Victoria Avenue between
OL,8,F6pm and 11pm.
OL,10,FFriday 5 June will see the first
OL,11,Fcompetitive event of the festival.
OL,13,FCars and motorbikes will race in "The
OL,14,FMoonlight Sprint" along Victoria
OL,15,FAvenue, reaching speeds of up to
OL,16,F120mph.
OL,18,FThe sprint Regulations allow for
OL,19,Fclassic and modern vehicles to compete.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
