OL,3,CThe Jersey International Motoring
OL,4,CFestival returns for 2026
OL,6,FDuring the weekend, a "festival hub"
OL,7,Fwill open in People's Park and Lower
OL,8,FPark. There will be food stalls, live
OL,9,Fmusic, and other entertainment on
OL,10,Foffer alongside traditional car
OL,11,Fdisplays.
OL,13,FOn Sunday 7 June, Victoria Park will
OL,14,Ftransform into the 'Active Area' where
OL,15,Fdrivers will display the power of
OL,16,Ftheir vehicles with burnouts and
OL,17,Fdoughnuts.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
