OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1780513862
OL,3,CThe Jersey International Motoring
OL,4,CFestival returns for 2026
OL,6,FThat night, the grand finale will see
OL,7,Fthe event culminate in the Westmount
OL,8,FHillclimb with the fastest vehicles
OL,9,Fracing against the clock.
OL,11,FA #30 million car?
OL,13,FThe main attraction of the
OL,14,FInternational Festival has always been
OL,15,Fthe cars, from supercars like
OL,16,FLamborghinis and Ferraris, to pre-war
OL,17,Fvintage motors like the Peterson
OL,18,FBentley and 30s Sprint car.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/9
