OL,3,CThe Jersey International Motoring
OL,4,CFestival returns for 2026
OL,6,FThis year, a one-of-a-kind Jaguar XJ-
OL,7,F13 prototype will be on show. The car
OL,8,Fwas originally designed to compete at
OL,9,FLe Mans in the 1960s, but it took too
OL,10,Flong to produce.
OL,12,FThe racer is normally housed at the
OL,13,FBritish Motor Museum in the UK and has
OL,14,Fa V12 engine with more than 500
OL,15,Fhorsepower.
OL,17,FIt's owned by The Jaguar Daimler
OL,18,FHeritage Trust, and although it is
OL,19,Festimated to be worth #30 million, it
OL,20,Fwill almost certainly never be sold.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/9
